settings.title: Ambassador
settings.subtitle: Alpha Prime Brand Ambassador program offers an exclusive membership to prime athletes globally who are leaders in their community and are passionately engaged in promoting fashion, active & healthy lifestyles. The ideal Brand Ambassador is active, energetic, hard-working and outgoing, with a strong engagement in a variety of networks and organizations. Apply to become an Ambassador.

settings.title: I want to cancel my order
settings.subtitle: To cancel your order, please refer to our Returns and Exchanges page here.

settings.title: I want to change my order
settings.subtitle: To cancel your order, please refer to our Returns and Exchanges page here.

settings.title: I received the wrong item
settings.subtitle: If you have received the wrong item, please refer to our Return and Exchanges page here.

settings.title: I received a defective item
settings.subtitle: If you have received a defective item, please refer to our Return and Exchanges page here.

settings.title: Can you deliver to PO Box's?
settings.subtitle: Products that use standard shipping can be shipped to a PO Box. Expedited and Premium delivery do not deliver to PO Boxes.

settings.title: Customs & Import Fees
settings.subtitle: Import duties and taxes are not included in our shipping charges and may be charged upon delivery. Please check with your customs office to learn more about your duties and taxes.

settings.title: International Delivery
settings.subtitle: Alpha Prime Products are available for International Delivery. Please refer to our Shipping page for more information.

settings.title: I need to return something
settings.subtitle: Items must be returned within 30 days from the day you've received your order and must be accompanied by the original packing slip, order number, and receipt. Your credit card account will be credited the appropriate amount upon processing of the returned item(s).

settings.title: Return Policy
settings.subtitle: For inquiries regarding our return policy please refer to our Returns and Exchanges Page here.

settings.title: Military Discount
settings.subtitle: Military Discount

settings.title: Responders Discount
settings.subtitle: Responders Discount

settings.title: Refunds
settings.subtitle: Once your return is received and inspected, we will send you an email to notify you that we have received your returned item. We will also notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund. If you are approved, then your refund will be processed, and a credit will automatically be applied to your credit card or original method of payment, within a certain amount of days.

settings.title: This item was on sale previously, can I get it at the sale price?
settings.subtitle: For inquiries regarding items previously on sale, fill out our contact form to get in touch with a customer service representative.

settings.title: How can I pay for my order?
settings.subtitle: We accept Google Pay, PayPal, Apple Pay, Visa, Mastercard, AMEX, and Discover.

settings.title: Gift Cards
settings.subtitle:
If you purchase a gift card through our website, a unique code will be emailed to the email address you entered at check out.

We currently do not offer physical gift cards.
